Even Higher is a book describing the future of TV broadcasting, as predicted by various industry figures.
Published in 2012 by Broadgate Publications in Richmond, UK, Even Higher is the follow-up volume to High Above - The untold story of Astra, Europe’s leading satellite company, which describes the birth and growth of the European satellite provider SES, and was published by Broadgate Publications in 2010 for SES’ 25th anniversary.
It is a large “coffee table” style book (32 x 24cm) of 176 pages with hundreds of photographs.
